(Enjoy Learning, Make Our History)

8
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:39,220
(Zhongqiao)

9
00:00:45,020 --> 00:00:47,180
(Signature of Party A: Yu Luo)

10
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:50,060
OK?

11
00:00:50,330 --> 00:00:51,170
Miss Yu,

12
00:00:51,610 --> 00:00:52,500
Mr. Liao asked you

13
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:53,960
to call him every week as it will

14
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,750
take you long to pay all his money.

15
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:56,600
I'll remember.

16
00:00:58,850 --> 00:01:01,630
♪Wake up and realize all is in vain♪

17
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:02,640
She's still so mean.

18
00:01:03,930 --> 00:01:05,700
Why does Mr. Liao like her?

19
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:07,300
(Thinking about my past life,)

20
00:01:07,460 --> 00:01:10,060
(I'm afraid I borrowed more than that.)

21
00:01:10,330 --> 00:01:11,600
(No matter what he did,)

22
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:13,160
(I still have to pay him back.)

23
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:15,560
Didn't you promise to pick me up?

24
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:16,840
Yihao,

25
00:01:16,970 --> 00:01:19,400
I'm afraid to see Mr. Liao's men.

26
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,660
Just come and pick me up.

27
00:01:20,730 --> 00:01:22,330
(Did he let them go so soon?)

28
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:25,000
Even if you're not worried about me,

29
00:01:25,300 --> 00:01:27,160
think about the baby in my belly.

30
00:01:27,330 --> 00:01:28,760
It's your baby.

31
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:31,260
OK, I'll see you at home tonight.

32
00:01:31,660 --> 00:01:32,760
Come home early.

33
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,100
(At home?)

34
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:37,500
(They live together, but I didn't notice.)

35
00:01:41,170 --> 00:01:42,010
Luo.

36
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,680
Luo, what are you doing here?

37
00:01:45,330 --> 00:01:47,500
Luo, are you still drunk?

38
00:01:47,730 --> 00:01:48,980
It's me, Yueru,

39
00:01:49,230 --> 00:01:50,450
your best friend.

40
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,820
Yeah, best friend.

41
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:54,560
Luo, you know what,

42
00:01:54,750 --> 00:01:56,270
if you hadn't talked nonsense that night,

43
00:01:56,710 --> 00:01:58,510
we could have got you out of there.

44
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,330
In the end, we were detained by Mr. Liao

45
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,710
and were questioned for days.

46
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:04,400
How did you know I was in danger?

47
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,240
I...

48
00:02:06,220 --> 00:02:07,560
We heard about it.

49
00:02:07,940 --> 00:02:10,200
Luo, why did you do that?

50
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:12,280
You should have told us you were bullied.

51
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:13,930
Now, look,

52
00:02:13,930 --> 00:02:14,930
what you did have made you

53
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,170
suffer for nothing.

54
00:02:16,650 --> 00:02:17,740
(Suffer for nothing?)

55
00:02:18,270 --> 00:02:20,220
(It's a pity you didn't make money, right?)

56
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,500
(We'll settle the score later.)

57
00:02:23,130 --> 00:02:24,600
Luo, why are you walking so fast?

58
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,880
I'm saying this for your own good.

59
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,060
We're going to have some fun.

60
00:02:31,370 --> 00:02:32,210
What?

61
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,190
- I told you.
- Chen Yihao!

62
00:02:36,330 --> 00:02:37,460
What are you doing together?

63
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,360
None of your business.

64
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:41,360
Why isn't it my business?

65
00:02:41,650 --> 00:02:43,370
Chen Yihao has a girlfriend.

66
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,100
You unethical mistress!

67
00:02:45,110 --> 00:02:46,360
Who are you calling a mistress?

68
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,130
How dare she hang up on me again?

69
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,560
You two must make it clear today.

70
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,660
Do I have to tell you who I'm dating?

71
00:02:56,660 --> 00:02:58,280
Miss Yu may be busy,

72
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,200
Mr. Liao.

73
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,990
Ask her out for dinner some other time.

74
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:03,300
Is she busy?

75
00:03:03,550 --> 00:03:06,520
They set me up last night.

76
00:03:06,650 --> 00:03:08,390
Something was wrong with the wine.

77
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:10,350
Let someone find out what she's up to.

78
00:03:10,740 --> 00:03:11,580
Yes.

79
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,060
Wang Yueru,

80
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,750
you live in my rented apartment

81
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:23,960
and you're mean to me.

82
00:03:26,050 --> 00:03:26,970
Luo.

83
00:03:27,690 --> 00:03:29,930
Yihao, you're back.

84
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:34,500
Yihao, you're wrong about me.

85
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,800
Before you came over,

86
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:38,310
Liao Youting answered a call.

87
00:03:38,530 --> 00:03:40,140
He knew there would be reporters.

88
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:42,050
He tried to protect his Group's reputation,

89
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,000
so he made me say that.

90
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,030
What?

91
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,600
You don't know

92
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,290
how much I suffered

93
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:51,480
to save you.

94
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,930
If I hadn't promised to stay with him,

95
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,590
he wouldn't have let you go.

96
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,440
Luo,

97
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,760
I'm sorry.

98
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:01,500
I didn't want this to happen.

99
00:04:01,730 --> 00:04:02,570
Yihao,

100
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,120
don't mention it again.

101
00:04:07,980 --> 00:04:08,820
Luo,

102
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:12,060
Mi Shanshan came to me today.

103
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,530
I know.

104
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:16,000
She came to me too.

105
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:17,530
And it got physical.

106
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,600
She hit you?

107
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:20,950
What a monster is she?

108
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:22,310
She's just like Liao Youting.

109
00:04:23,210 --> 00:04:24,570
We can't afford to mess with her.

110
00:04:27,620 --> 00:04:29,080
You're right.

111
00:04:29,470 --> 00:04:31,130
Mi Shanshan has been pestering me.

112
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,500
Her family is powerful.

113
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,800
I have no choice.

114
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:36,100
But Luo, you know

115
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:37,560
I only love you.

116
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:39,130
Yeah.

117
00:04:39,730 --> 00:04:41,060
I believe you.

118
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,530
Then why are you with Liao Youting?

119
00:04:44,910 --> 00:04:47,050
He let me be with him.

120
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:49,130
Just like you,

121
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,560
I have no choice.

122
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,640
Yihao, you know,

123
00:04:52,650 --> 00:04:53,960
I love you so much.

124
00:04:54,650 --> 00:04:56,760
I know you want to start a company.

125
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,460
So,

126
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:00,310
Mi Shanshan can help you.

127
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:03,320
And I'll be waiting for you.

128
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:04,830
Luo,

129
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,310
you're so understanding.

130
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:08,630
Don't worry.

131
00:05:08,770 --> 00:05:10,430
I won't let you down.

132
00:05:17,990 --> 00:05:20,260
You don't know

133
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,930
how much I suffered

134
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,900
after you left.

135
00:05:24,370 --> 00:05:26,020
He only let you go

136
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:27,740
because I promised to stay with him.

137
00:05:29,250 --> 00:05:31,160
(She knew they set her up.)

138
00:05:31,850 --> 00:05:32,690
(So...)

139
00:05:33,170 --> 00:05:34,330
(She is using me again?)

140
00:05:36,300 --> 00:05:38,380
(Enjoy Learning, Make Our History)

141
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:41,060
Yu Luo, I'm leaving tomorrow.

142
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:44,050
Wait for my news about your study abroad.

143
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,700
I'll see you off tomorrow.

144
00:05:46,740 --> 00:05:48,000
(Yan Lan, Professor of Economics)

145
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,760
I wanted to give you a parting gift,

146
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,870
but I didn't know what to give.

147
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,300
These are my notes from school.

148
00:05:53,330 --> 00:05:54,200
What's in there

149
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:55,460
should help you.

150
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,330
(Western Economics Final Review)
Don't mind my writing.

151
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,200
How could I?

152
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,690
Your handwriting is good, Professor.

153
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,040
See you tomorrow.

154
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,880
Yeah.

155
00:06:05,170 --> 00:06:06,950
♪I'm going to cross a distance♪

156
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,320
(It's the luckiest thing)

157
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:09,880
(to know Professor Yan.)

158
00:06:10,460 --> 00:06:11,330
(But the man)

159
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:14,980
(who's like a brother to me is leaving.)

160
00:06:15,260 --> 00:06:17,060
(Western Economics Final Review)

161
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,680
♪Close my eyes tightly♪

162
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:21,680
Mr. Liao,

163
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,730
the guys following Miss Yu said

164
00:06:23,730 --> 00:06:25,080
there's nothing unusual about her.

165
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:26,210
She stays at school most of the time.

166
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:28,940
Should we withdraw the guys?

167
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:30,140
No.

168
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:32,000
Keep an eye on her
in case she'll be in danger again.

169
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:32,960
There's no danger,

170
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,130
but you should know something.

171
00:06:34,470 --> 00:06:36,420
Miss Yu is applying to study abroad.

172
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,030
- Study abroad?
- Yes.

173
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:39,710
Her professor,

174
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,430
Yan Lan, helped her.

175
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:42,500
Yan Lan?

176
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:46,900
(Jixiang Airlines)

177
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:48,060
(Airport Lounge)
Yu Luo.

178
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,350
Professor, sorry to keep you waiting.

179
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,320
I was stuck in traffic.

180
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,360
It's OK.

181
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,160
Why did yo bring so little luggage?

182
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:56,350
I can buy whatever I need there.

183
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,730
Then let's get in.

184
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:58,590
Wait a minute.

185
00:06:58,990 --> 00:07:00,070
I have a friend to see me off.

186
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,040
A friend?

187
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,560
A friend who grew up with me.

188
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,640
Sit.

189
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:08,610
Your friend must be great, too.

190
00:07:08,710 --> 00:07:10,030
Yeah, he is great.

191
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:12,500
Here he is.

192
